I read some great books in 2023.

My favourite fiction book was [The Mountain in the Sea](https://matt.routleynet.org/2023/09/16/finished-reading-the.html) by Ray Nayler. Non-fiction was [Enemy of All Mankind](https://matt.routleynet.org/2023/05/09/finished-reading-enemy.html) by Steven Johnson. 

